From 39aa2a70213a831964d763dfd1dcd6a5f3410da1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ben Wagner <bungeman@google.com>
Date: Tue, 20 Jan 2026 16:37:04 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Move code out of SkPath_pathdata.cpp

SkPath_pathdata.cpp existed so that Skia could be compiled with the old
SkPathRef or the new SkPathData. Now that the old SkPathRef has been
removed the SkPathData can be used directly. This moves the contents of
SkPath_pathdata.cpp to the files the code naturally belongs to.

Change-Id: If48a82a4c7fce1ce9ac0b0b64278381ca2a60aa0
Reviewed-on: https://skia-review.googlesource.com/c/skia/+/1145998
Commit-Queue: Ben Wagner <bungeman@google.com>
Reviewed-by: Florin Malita <fmalita@google.com>
Signed-off-by: Hin-Tak Leung <htl10@users.sourceforge.net>
